OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FA solicitor is calling for a public
OL,7,Finquiry into Gwynedd Council's child
OL,8,Fsafeguarding measures.
OL,10,FKatherine Yates represents former
OL,11,Fpupils of Canolfan Brynffynnon, an
OL,12,Feducational unit in Y Felinheli for
OL,13,Fchildren with behavioural and
OL,14,Femotional needs which closed in 2014.
OL,16,FIn June 2026, Gwynedd Council
OL,17,Fapologised to pupils who attended the
OL,18,Funit, who have started to receive
OL,19,Fthousands of pounds' worth of
OL,20,Fcompensation as a result of their
OL,21,Fexperiences at the unit.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FAn investigation by current affairs
OL,7,Fprogramme Y Byd ar Bedwar has revealed
OL,8,Fthat 5 former pupils have received a
OL,9,Fpayment from insurers on behalf of the
OL,10,Fcouncil, with 14 other pupils in the
OL,11,Fprocess of bringing cases. These
OL,12,Fpayments are being made without any
OL,13,Fadmission of liability.
OL,15,FAsked whether she feels children are
OL,16,Fsafe under Gwynedd Council, Katherine
OL,17,FYates, who also represents the victims
OL,18,Fof Neil Foden, said:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,F"I'm afraid I would have to say no, I
OL,7,Fdon't think they are. I really think
OL,8,Fwe need a public enquiry into Gwynedd
OL,9,Fand how they are running their
OL,10,Fschools. When I look at how Gwynedd
OL,11,Fhas behaved through the years - with
OL,12,Fthe Foden case, with this case - I
OL,13,Fhave been really shocked."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FCanolfan Brynffynnon was closed
OL,7,Fsuddenly in 2014. A year later, Sion
OL,8,FBedwyr Evans, the unit's interim
OL,9,Fheadteacher, and Garry Vaughan
OL,10,FRoberts, a member of staff there, were
OL,11,Fcharged with 49 offences of cruelty
OL,12,Ftowards children between September
OL,13,F2006 and March 2014. Both denied the
OL,14,Fcharges, with a court case scheduled
OL,15,Ffor 2016, but the case was dropped
OL,16,Fafter the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,17,Freceived new evidence from the police,
OL,18,Fstating there was no realistic
OL,19,Fprospect of conviction.
OL,26,@oD@csw
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FThe charges came as a result of
OL,7,Fcomplaints from 24 pupils who spoke to
OL,8,FNorth Wales Police following the
OL,9,Fclosure of the unit. One of those was
OL,10,FDillon Roberts, an autistic young man
OL,11,Fwho attended the unit between 2010 and
OL,12,F2014 when he was a child.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,F"I was dragged into the headmaster's
OL,7,Foffice by this teacher and he
OL,8,Fbasically restrained me, so I couldn't
OL,9,Fmove or get out of the way or anything
OL,10,Flike that, and Mr Evans got the
OL,11,Fstrimmer and he got it right up my
OL,12,Fneck. And then he was getting right
OL,13,Fclose up to my hair, and I could feel
OL,14,Fthe wind-rush off the actual nylon
OL,15,Fstrings on my hair."
OL,17,FDillon added: "If you did something
OL,18,Fwrong, you were forced into a goal,
OL,19,Fand one of the teachers would kick a
OL,20,Fball really hard at your backside."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FGarry Roberts and Sion Bedwyr Evans
OL,7,Fdenied the charges ahead of a court
OL,8,Fcase that was scheduled for 2016; but
OL,9,Fin March of that year, the case was
OL,10,Fdropped. The Crown Prosecution Service
OL,11,Fsaid this was due to new evidence from
OL,12,Fthe police, and that there was no
OL,13,Frealistic prospect of conviction.
OL,15,FSion Bedwyr Evans said that the
OL,16,Fallegations as presented do not
OL,17,Faccurately reflect the facts, and that
OL,18,Fthe evidence that caused the case to
OL,19,Fbe dropped in 2016 speaks for itself.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FHe added: "This contains exculpatory
OL,7,Fmaterial as to the veracity of the
OL,8,Fallegations being made against myself
OL,9,Fand a co worker as well as to the
OL,10,Fintegrity of those making them. The
OL,11,Fallegations as presented do not
OL,12,Faccurately reflect the true facts"
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
