PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FGarry Roberts said that during Gwynedd
OL,7,FCouncil's investigation, evidence of
OL,8,Fmisconduct was found regarding
OL,9,Fallegations concerning an unsuitable
OL,10,Fball game referred to as "bumsies"
OL,11,Fbeing played at the unit. The
OL,12,Fconclusion of the Council's
OL,13,Fdisciplinary process was that he
OL,14,Freceived a final written warning that
OL,15,Flasted 18 months.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FBoth Bedwyr Evans and Garry Roberts
OL,7,Falso say that, after the criminal case
OL,8,Fwas dropped, they complained to the
OL,9,FIOPC - the Independent Office for
OL,10,FPolice Conduct - about the way the
OL,11,FNorth Wales Police investigation was
OL,12,Fconducted.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FThey say that some complaints were
OL,7,Fupheld by North Wales Police,
OL,8,Fincluding questions about the police
OL,9,Finterviews and the gathering of
OL,10,Fevidence. This, they say, was the new
OL,11,Fevidence the CPS gave when dropping
OL,12,Fthe case in 2016. However, despite us
OL,13,Fmaking several inquiries to North
OL,14,FWales Police, the IOPC, and the CPS,
OL,15,Fthey were not able to provide
OL,16,Fclarification regarding these
OL,17,Fcomplaints.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
