PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FA year after the criminal case was
OL,7,Fdropped, Brenda, Dillon's mother,
OL,8,Freceived a letter from Gwynedd
OL,9,FCouncil's Children and Supporting
OL,10,FFamilies department. After taking
OL,11,Flegal action against the council, in
OL,12,FMay 2026, he received #12,000 in
OL,13,Fcompensation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
