PN,43913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FY Byd ar Bedwar has spoken with
OL,7,Fseveral parents who have brought legal
OL,8,Fcases against Gwynedd Council
OL,9,Ffollowing their children's experiences
OL,10,Fat Canolfan Brynffynnon, revealing
OL,11,Fthat two former pupils received
OL,12,Fcompensation as early as 2019. The
OL,13,Fparents of one of the former pupils
OL,14,Fwho received compensation say they
OL,15,Fraised concerns with Gwynedd Council
OL,16,Fin 2010 - four years before Canolfan
OL,17,FBrynffynnon closed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FKatherine Yates added: "These parents,
OL,7,Fthey complained, lots of them. But
OL,8,Fnothing happened. When I look at the
OL,9,Fway Gwynedd Council has behaved with
OL,10,Fthe (Neil) Foden case, and this case,
OL,11,Fit shocks me."
OL,13,FThrough her research into the case,
OL,14,FKatherine claims that Gwynedd Council
OL,15,Fcontinued to pay the salaries of the
OL,16,Ftwo accused members of staff for 9
OL,17,Fyears while they were suspended from
OL,18,Ftheir posts.
OL,26,@rD@EpmrD@JpnsD@NO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,F"How much has that cost the taxpayer?
OL,7,FAnd why should they pay that while
OL,8,FGwynedd Council fails to follow its
OL,9,Fown rules?"
OL,11,FY Byd ar Bedwar asked Gwynedd Council
OL,12,Fto discuss the Canolfan Brynffynnon
OL,13,Fcase, but instead they sent a
OL,14,Fstatement.
OL,16,FIt says that no child should tolerate
OL,17,Fabuse of any kind, and although these
OL,18,Fcases go back a few years, the Council
OL,19,Fapologises to former pupils.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,F"In the case of Canolfan Brynffynnon,
OL,7,Fwhich closed in 2014, it came to light
OL,8,Fthat pupils had been abused. A joint
OL,9,Finvestigation was conducted between
OL,10,FGwynedd Council and North Wales Police
OL,11,Fwhich led to a criminal case along
OL,12,Fwith the implementation of child
OL,13,Fprotection procedures."
OL,15,F"The criminal case did not proceed and
OL,16,Fover the following years, the Council
OL,17,Fconducted a number of investigations
OL,18,Fand reviews into what happened."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,F"A new review of all the steps taken
OL,7,Fat that time has already been
OL,8,Fcommissioned by the Council to ensure
OL,9,Fthat any lessons learned at the time
OL,10,Fcontinue to be implemented today."
OL,12,FY Byd ar Bedwar also got confirmation
OL,13,Ffrom the council that it commissioned
OL,14,Fan independent review last December of
OL,15,Fall the steps taken at the time, which
OL,16,Fhas almost reached its conclusion.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,FThe council added: "By today, every
OL,7,Faspect of child safeguarding
OL,8,Farrangements in Gwynedd has been
OL,9,Fcompletely reviewed and strengthened
OL,10,Fin line with the recommendations of
OL,11,Fthe Our Bravery Brought Justice report
OL,12,Fpublished in 2025. This will continue
OL,13,Fto be a top priority for Gwynedd
OL,14,FCouncil"
OL,16,FRegarding Mrs. Yates' claim that
OL,17,FGwynedd Council paid the salaries of
OL,18,Fstaff who were suspended for a period
OL,19,Fof 9 years, the council said:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43919
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,F"While we cannot comment on employment
OL,7,Fmatters relating to members of staff
OL,8,For former members of staff, we
OL,9,Frecognize that this case has taken an
OL,10,Funacceptably long period and apologize
OL,11,Ffor that. Although the complex and
OL,12,Funique circumstances of the cases
OL,13,Fcontributed to the delay, these
OL,14,Fmatters should have been resolved much
OL,15,Fsooner."
OL,17,FIn response to Mrs. Yates' claim,
OL,18,FGarry Roberts said:
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G19/20
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43920
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781722095
OL,3,CCall for public inquiry into Gwynedd
OL,4,CCouncil's child safeguarding measures
OL,6,F"I had no control over the length of
OL,7,Ftime Cyngor Gwynedd kept me suspended
OL,8,Ffrom my post."
OL,10,FWatch Y Byd ar Bedwar: Taliadau Tawel
OL,11,FBrynffynnon, June 15th on S4C, S4C
OL,12,FClic, BBC iPlayer, and S4C's YouTube
OL,13,Fchannel.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G20/20
